In order to install the Aggregator component:

Create a directory within the home directory from which you wish the aggregator to run.

Pull installer.sh from the github to this directory.

Run installer.sh with sudo permissions to prepare the environment.

installer.sh will pull all nessessary files from Github, as well as installing needed programs and placing files in the correct directories

To start the Aggregator, once the installer has run, exectue starter.sh which the installer will have pulled from the github into the same directory
